Project tested locally and runs perfectly as producer is able to send messages for consumer to recieve and print on console. 
Project consist of 2 console applications (KafkaProducerClient and KafkaConsumerClient).

Can also be tested on postman while server is running for an api response.

ASP.NET Core 3.1
IDE: Rider
Name of Topic: temp-topic-Kafka-Topic-1 and running on localhost:9092
POST URL: https://localhost:5001/kafka/send?topic=temp-topic-Kafka-Topic-1
JSON object to be passed:
{
    "Id":1,
    "Name":"Richard",
    "Message":"Test Notification"    
}
